metadata.bio:
The Turboprops are a band formed in summer 2006 in El Paso, TX out of the ashes of Los Skattackers by George Salas and Aaron Stillman (formerly of Politically Corrupt.) Joe-Ray Lopez and Caesar Sanchez were added shortly after. They also frequently play wiht Atom from The Intellijents.

Their music catalog tends to be diverse, but is centered around punk, powerpop and ska.
